# WhatsApp Transcriber - Environment Variables
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys
# These are OPTIONAL - you can also enter API keys in the UI

# ==========================================
# Transcription API Keys (Optional)
# ==========================================

# Mistral API Key (for Voxtral Mini transcription)
# Get your key from: https://console.mistral.ai/
# Cost: ~$0.001/minute (~$0.06/hour)
# MISTRAL_API_KEY=your_mistral_api_key_here

# ==========================================
# AI Enhancement API Keys (Optional)
# ==========================================

# Anthropic Claude API Key
# Get your key from: https://console.anthropic.com
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_claude_api_key_here

# OpenAI API Key
# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# ==========================================
# Notes:
# ==========================================
#
# - Mistral API key is only needed if using Voxtral Mini transcription
# - AI enhancement keys are only needed if you want to use AI correction
# - Ollama (local) does NOT require an API key
# - Never commit your .env file to version control
# - Keys in .env file take precedence over UI input
# - Remove the # at the start of the line to activate a variable
